latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Simple 3 step night routine by @seeloveindia 
✅ cleansing oil 
✅ exfoliating serum 
✅ nightcream 
Super impressive Indian brand 
Have u tried it ? If u haven’t head to their website and avail a 25% discount 😉😘

This #messymaharani went to #jaipur wearing @raw_mango with a jacket from @louisvuitton but that’s not what we here for 

I’ve always loved travelling through #rajasthan except for my last bad experience at a property u can read about somewhere on this page .. 

@amanbagh in Jaipur has restored my faith in Rajasthani service .. 
the food was outstanding ♥️
The service was impeccable ♥️ 
If you planning a trip through Rajasthan please put this place on your wish list 

I was lucky my friend had a big birthday and I got to go there and the place is worth the 2hr drive from the city ♥️ 

The staff is so well trained I could ask for 5 things at a time and still be served all 5 impeccably ♥️ 

The bath tub was bigger than I could imagine but that u can obviously see on their website for me it’s the little things that matter 

The Rudraksha or agarbattis on ur pillows .. the hot water bottles left next to ur bed cause some people feel cold even with central heating.. or the fact that every time u leave your room someone magically cleans it ♥️ 

I also loved the fact that before going we had to send our ids to a point person at the hotel and day 2 of our trip she personally WhatsApp messaged each of us if our stay was going ok and we needed anything ♥️ 

I call that the best kinda service- non intrusive, polite and helpful.. 
most hotels can learn from them the art of never ringing a door bell or be in anyones face .. 

I can’t wait to go back and this time for longer ♥️

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
#ad 
It's that time of the year to Glow Up! The weather is changing and so are my skincare needs. Here are my go to favourite face elixirs from @rasluxuryoils, an Elixir for every skin need.

On the days my acne is acting up I use the Luminous face clearing elixir, it's a myth that acne skin cannot handle oil based products. My skin loves this!

The Radiance 24K Gold Face Elixir for days when I need that extra glow. It’s enriched with actual gold flakes and the goodness of rosehip, saffron and many potent, natural ingredients.

For my night time routine my usual go to is the revival or infinity face elixirs. I wake up to a skin that feels supple, plump and glowy. 

I cannot wait for you guys to try them out.
